PHASE 1: PRE-LAUNCH (WEEK 0)
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
Goal: Get everything ready to launch
Time: 7 days
Cost: $100-200

DAY 1: LEGAL & BUSINESS SETUP
─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

□ Form LLC (if not done yet)
  - File with your state: $100-150
  - Get EIN from IRS (free): irs.gov/ein
  - Open business bank account

□ Protect Your IP
  - Add copyright notices to all files
  - Create LICENSE.txt
  - Document your creation process
  - See IP_PROTECTION_COMPLETE.txt for details

□ Set Up Accounting
  - QuickBooks Self-Employed (free 30 days)
  - Or Wave Accounting (free forever)
  - Create categories: Revenue, API costs, Marketing, Hosting

□ Get Business Email
  - yourname@contractreview.com
  - Use Google Workspace ($6/month) or Zoho (free)

DAY 2: PAYMENT & BILLING SETUP
─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

□ Create Stripe Account
  1. Go to stripe.com
  2. Sign up with business info
  3. Verify bank account (1-2 day wait)
  4. Create products:
     - Monthly Plan: $49/month recurring
     - Annual Plan: $149/year recurring

□ Integrate Stripe into Your App
  - Add payment page to your Flask app
  - Or use Stripe Payment Links (easier)
  - Test with Stripe test mode first

□ Set Up Subscription Management
  - Decide: Stripe Billing Portal or custom
  - Enable customer self-service cancellation
  - Set up email notifications

□ Prepare Invoices
  - Stripe auto-generates invoices
  - Add your company info to Stripe settings
  - Configure receipt emails

DAY 3: HOSTING & INFRASTRUCTURE
─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

□ Choose Production Hosting
  Option A: PythonAnywhere ($5/month)
  Option B: Heroku ($7/month) 
  Option C: DigitalOcean ($6/month)
  Recommendation: Start with PythonAnywhere

□ Set Up Production Environment
  - Deploy app to hosting
  - Configure environment variables (API keys)
  - Set up custom domain (yourproduct.com)
  - Enable HTTPS/SSL (free with Let's Encrypt)
  - Test everything works

□ Set Up Monitoring
  - UptimeRobot (free) - monitors if site is down
  - Google Analytics (free) - tracks visitors
  - Stripe Dashboard - tracks revenue
  - Set up email alerts for downtime

□ Create Backup Strategy
  - Daily code backups to GitHub
  - Database backups (if you add one)
  - Export customer list weekly

