⚠️ COMMON PITFALLS TO AVOID
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

1. ❌ PERFECTIONISM
Don't wait to launch. Ship now, improve later.

2. ❌ UNDERPRICING
$49/month is fair. Don't go lower. Value your work.

3. ❌ IGNORING CUSTOMERS
Talk to every customer. Get feedback. Improve constantly.

4. ❌ TRYING EVERYTHING
Pick 2-3 marketing channels. Master them. Then expand.

5. ❌ NO RUNWAY
Keep 3-6 months expenses saved. Don't quit your job yet.

6. ❌ FEATURE CREEP
Don't build features until 10+ customers ask for them.

7. ❌ GIVING UP TOO SOON
Takes 50-100 conversations to get first 10 customers. Keep going!

